{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        Majority-to-Minority Transfer Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission.confirmationNumber }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
    Hi {{ submission.email }},

    Guardian of {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }}

    RE: Majority-to-Minority Transfer Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission.confirmationNumber }}

    Your application for a Majority-to-Minority Student Transfer for {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }} for {{ submission.enrollmentPeriod }} has been approved for the following two choices:

        1. Your student can be Wait Listed for his/her first choice: {{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }}. Should additional spaces become available at {{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }}, those spaces will be filled by students on the Wait List based on each student’s lottery number.  If spaces become available at {{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }} and your student is selected for a space based on his/her lottery number, our office will contact you and award your student a space at this school. Please note that the Wait List expires on July 15, {{ submission.enrollmentPeriod.afterLotteryEndingDate|date("Y") }}.

        2. Your student has been accepted for placement at his/her second choice: {{ submission.awardedSchoolID.formattedString }}

    You may only choose one of the above options.

    You have two choices for accepting or declining one of the options above:

        1. You may go online at url below to accept or decline your option.
        {{ url( 'stw_lottery_accept' , { uniqueID: submission.url } ) }}

        2. You may call TCS Attendance Office, Monday-Friday between 8:30am and 4:00pm, for instructions regarding accepting or declining by phone.


    Deadline to Accept or Decline

    {{ acceptOnlineDate }}; {{ acceptOnlineTime }} online

    OR

    {{ acceptOfflineDate }}; {{ acceptOfflineTime }} by phone

    IMPORTANT: If you do not accept or decline online or by phone by {{ acceptOnlineDate }}, your transfer and wait list options will automatically be declined; your student will not be allowed to transfer; and must attend the school for which they are zoned.

    Please save this email and/or record this confirmation number for your records.

    Please add choice@tusc.k12.al.us to your address list to ensure you receive future status updates of your application.

    This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies. If you have any questions regarding the Majority-to-Minority student transfer process, please contact TCS Attendance Office.

    Thanks,
    Tuscaloosa City Schools
{% endblock body_text %}

